These are teh steps in Centos07 to assign a Static IP Address to your network

Type this command to view your network IP Address

# ip a

Create a file named /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0 as follows:
DEVICE=eth0
BOOTPROTO=none
ONBOOT=yes
PREFIX=24
IPADDR=192.168.2.203
Restart network service: systemctl restart network


Here is a copy of my "ifcfg-eth0" file.

